我先知自己有幾on9 咁我果皮幾野點呢 忍唔q住打比佢問佢還錢 又話無錢又話d野唔係自己買 重要同我講借左大佬錢 要還比佢先<br />\n<br />\n屌 錢唔還都算9數 上星期重話卟完冰搞左兄弟條女？ 真係忍無可忍 你係咪hi大左呀？呀神經哥 你個女都5歲幾啦 e+搞d咁既野 重要搞兄弟條女 我點撐你呀 你無撚野呀<br />\n<br />\n神經哥姓李 佢老婆姓邱 我一問幾時還錢 兩個即刻del我fd 真係好野 佢地住紅磡 個女讀家維村間幼稚園<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/11/232031_8c75320bc4320a7c48253bca5472cecb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F11%2F232031_8c75320bc4320a7c48253bca5472cecb.png&h=41809e63&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/11/232107_4ea93b5283cf884c7d94e01f2ec7de6d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F11%2F232107_4ea93b5283cf884c7d94e01f2ec7de6d.png&h=7d711b4e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/11/232205_4bcf5e9a29f5c1120c39a969c80baa62.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F11%2F232205_4bcf5e9a29f5c1120c39a969c80baa62.png&h=34021079&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/11/232208_4bcf5e9a29f5c1120c39a969c80baa62.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F11%2F232208_4bcf5e9a29f5c1120c39a969c80baa62.png&h=e7d152d2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f61da8fe3e7f47012124d26c342f023834c728f7","tid":589020,"uid":31927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T15:28:51.000Z","msg":"lmlmlm"},{"pid":"9e0b1123073c63e610c35646193a9c0d9b98b6a8","tid":589020,"uid":127494,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T15:32:40.000Z","msg":"萬3你都肯借...真係好兄弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n留名"},{"pid":"12bc1497ec2179b9fac88e3d7cda6796dc27b1a2","tid":589020,"uid":706,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T15:33:45.000Z","msg":"沒有最5p 只有更5p<img sr